 2415
R.Capote, E.Soukhovitskii, J.M.Quesada, S.Chiba
Unpublished.
Lane consistent dispersive CC neutron OMP for incident energies between 1 keV
and 200 MeV for U-238. Gives lower reaction above 5 MeV. Local Fermi En used.
Model 4: GS rigid rotor + dynamical deformations (OPTMAN should be used).

